column16: Chris Young pops out to second baseman Edgar Gonzalez.
Miguel Montero doubles (7) on a line drive to right fielder Brian Giles.
Mark Reynolds homers (14) on a fly ball to right field.    Felipe Lopez scores.    Ryan Roberts scores.
Stephen Drew pops out to catcher Nick Hundley.
Gerardo Parra out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher Josh Wilson to first baseman Adrian Gonzalez.    Felipe Lopez to 2nd.
Felipe Lopez singles on a line drive to center fielder Tony Gwynn.
Darnell McDonald grounds into double play, shortstop Augie Ojeda to second baseman Ryan Roberts to first baseman Josh Whitesell.    Paul Janish out at 2nd.
Adam Rosales flies out to right fielder Justin Upton.
